import React from 'react';
import { BrowserRouter as Router, Routes, Route, Link } from 'react-router-dom';
import { Box, Typography, Grid, Paper } from '@mui/material';
import QueueVisualizerPage from './pages/QueueVisualizerPage';
import ArrayAlgorithmsPage from './pages/ArrayAlgorithmsPage';
import KadanesAlgorithmPage from './pages/array-algorithms/kadanes-algorithm';
import PrefixSumPage from './pages/array-algorithms/prefix-sum';
import SlidingWindowPage from './pages/array-algorithms/sliding-window';
import HashingPage from './pages/array-algorithms/hashing';
import FrequencyCountPage from './pages/array-algorithms/frequency-count';

function App() {
  return (
    <Router>
      <Box sx={{ bgcolor: 'primary.main', color: 'white', mb: 2 }}>
        <Box sx={{ maxWidth: 1200, mx: 'auto', px: 2, py: 1 }}>
          <Grid container alignItems="center" spacing={2}>
            <Grid item>
              <Typography variant="h6" component="div">
                DSA Visualizer
              </Typography>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item>
              <Link to="/" style={{ color: 'white', textDecoration: 'none', marginRight: 16 }}>
                Home
              </Link>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item>
              <Link to="/queue" style={{ color: 'white', textDecoration: 'none', marginRight: 16 }}>
                Queue
              </Link>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item>
              <Link to="/array-algorithms" style={{ color: 'white', textDecoration: 'none' }}>
                Array Algorithms
              </Link>
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
        </Box>
      </Box>

      <Box sx={{ maxWidth: 1200, mx: 'auto', px: 2 }}>
        <Routes>
          <Route path="/" element={<ArrayAlgorithmsPage />} />
          <Route path="/queue" element={<QueueVisualizerPage />} />
          <Route path="/array-algorithms" element={<ArrayAlgorithmsPage />} />
          <Route path="/array-algorithms/kadanes-algorithm" element={<KadanesAlgorithmPage />} />
          <Route path="/array-algorithms/prefix-sum" element={<PrefixSumPage />} />
          <Route path="/array-algorithms/sliding-window" element={<SlidingWindowPage />} />
          <Route path="/array-algorithms/hashing" element={<HashingPage />} />
          <Route path="/array-algorithms/frequency-count" element={<FrequencyCountPage />} />
        </Routes>
      </Box>
    </Router>
  );
}

export default App;
